<title>20年來「佛經文學對中國小說影響」研究綜述=Summarization Study of Influence of Sutra Literature to China Novel in Twenty Years</title>
<author>王立; 黃艷燕</author>
<time_orig_str>2004</time_orig_str>
<geo_level1>廣東, 中國 [Guangdong, China]</geo_level1>
