<doc_content>
<Paragraph>佛教東傳對中國古代小說，尤其是宋前小說的影響，是全方位、多角度的，它涉及小說故事題材、情節結構、思想內容等方面，近二十年對佛教與小說關係的研究日益增多，研究對象也逐漸由整體研究發展到個案研究，有關宣佛小說的價值與定位也相應起了變化。
The influence that Buddhism to china archaic novel, especially to the novel before the dynasty of song is all-around and from many angles, and deal with the theme of novel, polt and structure, thought and content , etc. Near twenty years the study about the relationship between Buddhism and China novel is manifolded. The object of research is developed from integer to individual. The worth and orientation about the novel that publicize Buddhism is changed.</Paragraph>
